extendedInfo.description: "Run A Bypass" is a puzzle game in which your task to complete a bypass circuit to connect electrical terminals at the top-left and bottom-right of the board. The game is played against the clock.Winning games contributes to unlocking of new game modes - harder game difficulties - and to new themes.This is a standalone version of a mini-game from an upcoming interactive novel that I'm currently working on with my brother.Coming soon: more themes.Please feel free to e-mail me with any bug reports, requests, or questions!

reviews.title: Very good game
reviews.comment: Very good game, I really liked it. I couldn\'t really see much of a difficulty curve though, and reaching the last difficulty setting felt like a big grind.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Good game but timer kills the fun!
reviews.comment: Nice puzzle concept is similar to PLUMMER apps on market.  Unfortunately, it is not too highly polished and the timer makes it very aggravating.  It would be better if we had option to turn timer off for casual play that is more enjoyable.  I will uninstall and stick to PLUMMER 3 which is same style game but much better!
reviews.author: A Google User
